1
00:00:15,125 --> 00:00:18,708
[AKANE] What's happening?
Why can't I breathe?

2
00:00:18,791 --> 00:00:23,916
It almost feels as if...
something's sitting on my chest.

3
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:28,208
[BORSCHT] Wake up and feed me,
little girl. I'm starving.

4
00:00:30,291 --> 00:00:32,583
[AKANE]
C'mon, Borscht.

5
00:00:32,666 --> 00:00:35,833
Why am I the one you're
always picking on?

6
00:00:35,916 --> 00:00:37,083
What's your problem?

7
00:00:37,166 --> 00:00:39,083
There's still food left
over from last night.

8
00:00:39,166 --> 00:00:42,500
You need to just eat this.
And quit bugging me.

9
00:00:45,791 --> 00:00:48,666
I get it. You're
so dramatic, cat.

10
00:00:53,916 --> 00:00:57,250
You'd rather eat a plastic
bag than eat your food?

11
00:00:58,750 --> 00:01:00,166
Hey, Shiori.

12
00:01:00,250 --> 00:01:02,541
Can you ask the cat why he
likes chewing on plastic bags,

13
00:01:02,625 --> 00:01:05,208
but then turns his nose up at
the kitty kibble I feed him?

14
00:01:05,291 --> 00:01:06,333
[SHIORI]
Mh-hm.

15
00:01:09,041 --> 00:01:11,416
[SHIORI] It was nice of your
family to take in a stray cat

16
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:14,083
like me and give
me a proper home.

17
00:01:14,166 --> 00:01:16,666
But here's the deal. The
sub-par cat food being served

18
00:01:16,750 --> 00:01:19,000
under this roof has truly
been a disappointment.

19
00:01:19,083 --> 00:01:21,416
I expected so much more
from the royal family.

20
00:01:21,500 --> 00:01:23,375
I've found better
meals in dumpsters.

21
00:01:23,458 --> 00:01:24,875
[BORSCHT, SHIORI]
So what I'm trying to say

22
00:01:24,958 --> 00:01:26,666
is that I'd rather
eat a plastic bag

23
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:28,750
than the processed
pellets I'm being fed.

24
00:01:28,833 --> 00:01:30,375
The plastic actually
tastes better

25
00:01:30,458 --> 00:01:33,083
than whatever so called
"meat" is in your tasteless--

26
00:01:33,166 --> 00:01:34,541
You can stop, Shiori.

27
00:01:34,625 --> 00:01:36,250
I get the message.

28
00:03:17,708 --> 00:03:20,750
[KAREN]
My name is Karen Ayugase.

29
00:03:20,833 --> 00:03:23,708
Akane and I have been best
friends since we were little.

30
00:03:23,791 --> 00:03:27,708
So, of course, she's
my favorite Sakurada.

31
00:03:27,791 --> 00:03:28,791
Good morning!

32
00:03:28,875 --> 00:03:30,375
Right back at ya, Akane.

33
00:03:30,458 --> 00:03:32,500
We were worried you weren't
gonna make it today.

34
00:03:32,583 --> 00:03:35,125
Yeah, me too. I had to fly here.

35
00:03:35,208 --> 00:03:36,375
[FUKUSHINA yelps]

36
00:03:36,458 --> 00:03:37,958
I don't get why you're
always freaking out

37
00:03:38,041 --> 00:03:39,541
about getting here on time.

38
00:03:39,625 --> 00:03:42,333
It's no big deal to be tardy
to class every once in a while.

39
00:03:42,416 --> 00:03:43,875
Yeah. I know,

40
00:03:43,958 --> 00:03:46,375
but I'm hoping to win a perfect
attendance award this year.

41
00:03:46,458 --> 00:03:49,583
An award's not that
important when you have to...

42
00:04:03,666 --> 00:04:04,458
[KAREN]
Oh, no!

43
00:04:04,541 --> 00:04:05,750
Akane's not...

44
00:04:05,833 --> 00:04:07,666
[STUDENTS]
Wearing her skirt!

45
00:04:07,750 --> 00:04:09,375
[KAREN] There's no doubt
that the whole class noticed

46
00:04:09,458 --> 00:04:11,208
Akane's skirt was missing,

47
00:04:11,291 --> 00:04:13,916
but she went about her day
as if nothing was wrong.

48
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:16,500
So everyone kept quiet about
the elephant in the room.

49
00:04:16,583 --> 00:04:18,375
Nobody had the
guts to bring it up.

50
00:04:18,458 --> 00:04:20,041
So we all just went
along with it,

51
00:04:20,125 --> 00:04:22,750
as if none of us noticed the
half-dressed princess either.

52
00:04:22,833 --> 00:04:25,958
Even I didn't say anything to
her. Which is weird, right?

53
00:04:26,041 --> 00:04:27,583
I guess since our class
seems to have made

54
00:04:27,666 --> 00:04:31,083
some mental pact not to
mention it, I go with the flow.

55
00:04:31,166 --> 00:04:33,333
If everybody keeps quiet, then
we can get through the day

56
00:04:33,416 --> 00:04:34,416
without incident.

57
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:37,291
After all, ignorance is bliss.

58
00:04:37,375 --> 00:04:39,583
But this is too weird to ignore!

59
00:04:39,666 --> 00:04:43,125
Can I get away with quietly
asking her about the skirt?

60
00:04:43,208 --> 00:04:45,833
Course not! This is
Akane we're talking about.

61
00:04:45,916 --> 00:04:47,041
She would die of embarrassment

62
00:04:47,125 --> 00:04:48,708
if she really forgot
to wear her skirt.

63
00:04:48,791 --> 00:04:53,000
[AKANE] I'm too embarrassed
to live! Ah! I've died.

64
00:04:53,083 --> 00:04:54,875
[KAREN] She has to have
noticed a breeze going on

65
00:04:54,958 --> 00:04:56,333
down there by now.

66
00:04:56,416 --> 00:04:58,041
Is it possible that she came
to school without a skirt

67
00:04:58,125 --> 00:04:59,250
on purpose?

68
00:04:59,333 --> 00:05:01,000
Like maybe she's trying
to make a statement

69
00:05:01,083 --> 00:05:03,750
or start a "no pants"
fashion trend.

70
00:05:03,833 --> 00:05:05,166
How do I approach this?

71
00:05:05,250 --> 00:05:06,708
If she thinks I'm making
fun of her clothes,

72
00:05:06,791 --> 00:05:09,125
she'll be so hurt
that she could die!

73
00:05:10,166 --> 00:05:11,250
Hey, girl.

74
00:05:11,333 --> 00:05:12,416
Where on earth did
your skirt run off to?

75
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:15,000
[screaming]

76
00:05:15,083 --> 00:05:17,125
[KAREN] I can't have my
best friend dying on me!

77
00:05:17,208 --> 00:05:20,750
I am so confused.
What am I supposed to do?

78
00:05:20,833 --> 00:05:22,250
You okay, Karen?

79
00:05:22,333 --> 00:05:24,458
You've been acting kinda
weird all day long.

80
00:05:24,541 --> 00:05:27,583
[KAREN] How can she stand
there like nothing's wrong?

81
00:05:27,666 --> 00:05:30,541
Calm down. It's all
right. I'm okay.

82
00:05:30,625 --> 00:05:32,250
I'll just assume that
nobody has the guts

83
00:05:32,333 --> 00:05:35,625
to say anything about the skirt
to Akane, and that's that.

84
00:05:35,708 --> 00:05:37,166
Akane, quick question for ya,

85
00:05:37,250 --> 00:05:39,833
would you rather wear a skirt,
shorts, or a pair of pants?

86
00:05:39,916 --> 00:05:42,791
It doesn't really matter to
me as long as they're cute.

87
00:05:42,875 --> 00:05:45,875
C'mon, that's not true. You
have to have a preference.

88
00:05:45,958 --> 00:05:47,333
Okay.

89
00:05:47,416 --> 00:05:48,916
If I have to choose,

90
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,041
I guess I would take
a skirt over the others.

91
00:05:51,125 --> 00:05:52,916
[GIRLS]
Huh?

92
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:56,333
Oh, so you must be into
micro-minis then, huh?

93
00:05:56,416 --> 00:05:59,666
I guess so. Wait, why?

94
00:06:01,208 --> 00:06:03,291
[KAREN]
How are they only now noticing?

95
00:06:03,375 --> 00:06:04,458
[STUDENT B]
Am I crazy,

96
00:06:04,541 --> 00:06:06,791
or is Akane Sakurada
not wearing a skirt?

97
00:06:06,875 --> 00:06:08,083
No, you're not.

98
00:06:08,166 --> 00:06:09,125
Are you sure?

99
00:06:09,208 --> 00:06:09,750
[STUDENT B]
Huh?

100
00:06:09,833 --> 00:06:10,958
President?

101
00:06:11,041 --> 00:06:13,500
Be quiet! Do you want
people to hear you?

102
00:06:13,583 --> 00:06:15,125
Sorry. Just slipped.

103
00:06:15,208 --> 00:06:18,791
Are you guys 100% certain that
Akane's not wearing a skirt?

104
00:06:18,875 --> 00:06:20,416
Uh. I'm not sure.

105
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:22,208
I guess she could be
wearing a mini skirt

106
00:06:22,291 --> 00:06:23,666
that's hidden under her sweater.

107
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:26,708
We didn't want to get caught
staring at her, y'know?

108
00:06:26,791 --> 00:06:29,166
Well, then, there's no
way for you to know

109
00:06:29,250 --> 00:06:31,875
what's going on underneath
her shirt, now is there?

110
00:06:31,958 --> 00:06:34,625
Nope. You have no idea.

111
00:06:34,708 --> 00:06:36,041
Have you guys even
stopped to think

112
00:06:36,125 --> 00:06:37,625
that if Akane forgot her skirt,

113
00:06:37,708 --> 00:06:40,708
she might've forgotten to wear
what goes underneath it, too?

114
00:06:40,791 --> 00:06:42,208
[STUDENT D]
Hey, Kanade.

115
00:06:42,291 --> 00:06:44,666
Have you heard the rumors
floating throughout the school?

116
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:46,166
Rumors about what?

117
00:06:46,250 --> 00:06:48,250
That your little sister
Akane's walking around

118
00:06:48,333 --> 00:06:49,583
without a skirt on today.

119
00:06:49,666 --> 00:06:51,000
There's no way.

120
00:06:51,083 --> 00:06:52,583
I could see her
forgetting to wear it,

121
00:06:52,666 --> 00:06:54,458
but someone would've
told her by now.

122
00:06:54,541 --> 00:06:56,375
You aren't worried
about her at all?

123
00:06:56,458 --> 00:06:58,375
No, not in the slightest.

124
00:06:58,458 --> 00:07:00,041
Even if something were going on,

125
00:07:00,125 --> 00:07:02,250
Akane is old enough
to handle it herself.

126
00:07:02,333 --> 00:07:03,500
Okay then.

127
00:07:03,583 --> 00:07:04,666
I guess if you're sure

128
00:07:04,750 --> 00:07:06,166
then I shouldn't put
much stock into it--

129
00:07:06,250 --> 00:07:07,375
[thud]

130
00:07:07,458 --> 00:07:09,208
--[KANADE groaning]
--[STUDENT D] Kanade!

131
00:07:09,291 --> 00:07:11,833
[STUDENT D] Oh, yeah.
You're not worried at all.

132
00:07:11,916 --> 00:07:13,583
[AOI]
She's not wearing a skirt?

133
00:07:13,666 --> 00:07:16,291
That's right. And everybody's
talking about it.

134
00:07:16,375 --> 00:07:18,958
[SHIZURU] But we don't
know if it's true or not.

135
00:07:19,041 --> 00:07:21,583
I wonder who would start
such an odd rumor.

136
00:07:21,666 --> 00:07:25,083
[AOI] Guess I can text Akane
and ask her about it.

137
00:07:25,166 --> 00:07:26,166
[screaming]

138
00:07:26,250 --> 00:07:27,500
What's wrong, Akane?

139
00:07:27,583 --> 00:07:29,125
Ugh, what's the matter with me?

140
00:07:29,208 --> 00:07:30,875
[KAREN]
About time she realized!

141
00:07:30,958 --> 00:07:34,333
Aw. This sucks. I forgot to
bring my phone to school today.

142
00:07:34,416 --> 00:07:37,375
Well, that's not the only
thing you forgot to bring today.

143
00:07:37,458 --> 00:07:39,458
[ANNOUNCER]
Attention all students:

144
00:07:39,541 --> 00:07:41,833
Akane Sakurada from Class A,

145
00:07:41,916 --> 00:07:43,750
please come to the
student council room

146
00:07:43,833 --> 00:07:45,041
as soon as possible.

147
00:07:45,125 --> 00:07:47,583
The vice president would
like to speak with you.

148
00:07:47,666 --> 00:07:50,750
Kana wants to see me?
What is she up to?

149
00:07:50,833 --> 00:07:54,375
Using the PA system to call
me is kinda overkill.

150
00:07:54,458 --> 00:07:57,250
I'm gonna go up with
you, all right?

151
00:07:57,333 --> 00:07:59,666
You know, in case
somethings wrong.

152
00:07:59,750 --> 00:08:01,916
Please. I'll be okay.

153
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:04,958
You don't have to be so
protective of me, Karen.

154
00:08:05,041 --> 00:08:07,083
But you can join me
since you're worried.

155
00:08:07,166 --> 00:08:09,125
You'll notice that I'm much
more confident and less shy

156
00:08:09,208 --> 00:08:10,416
than I used to be.

157
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:11,875
[KAREN]
It's actually not your shyness

158
00:08:11,958 --> 00:08:14,083
that I'm concerned about today.

159
00:08:14,166 --> 00:08:16,250
[AKANE]
C'mon, let's head over.

160
00:08:16,333 --> 00:08:19,625
[FUKUSHINA] This is it.
The perfect opportunity.

161
00:08:19,708 --> 00:08:21,291
[STUDENT B]
The Akane Sakurada...

162
00:08:21,375 --> 00:08:24,250
[STUDENT C] Is walking to
the student council room!

163
00:08:24,333 --> 00:08:26,083
[FUKUSHINA] Everybody knows
the student council room

164
00:08:26,166 --> 00:08:28,333
is on the third floor
of the south tower.

165
00:08:28,416 --> 00:08:31,083
We are currently on the second
floor of the east tower.

166
00:08:31,166 --> 00:08:33,791
She'll have to go upstairs
to meet her sister.

167
00:08:33,875 --> 00:08:35,333
Which means...

168
00:08:38,666 --> 00:08:42,958
[MALE STUDENTS] Sneak a peek.
Sneak a peek. Sneak--

169
00:08:43,041 --> 00:08:44,875
I seriously can't
thank you enough

170
00:08:44,958 --> 00:08:46,583
for always being
there for me, Karen.

171
00:08:46,666 --> 00:08:48,416
That's what friends
are for, silly.

172
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:51,500
But, you're such a good friend I
could totally marry you one day.

173
00:08:51,583 --> 00:08:53,458
Wonder if you're my type.

174
00:08:56,375 --> 00:08:57,958
[MALE STUDENTS]
Sneak a peek.

175
00:08:58,041 --> 00:09:06,416
Sneak a peek. Sneak a peek.

176
00:09:06,500 --> 00:09:08,458
Maybe this isn't
a good idea, guys.

177
00:09:08,541 --> 00:09:11,625
Uh, I mean, she's royalty
for crying out loud!

178
00:09:11,708 --> 00:09:14,416
It's crude! Not to
mention disrespectful!

179
00:09:14,500 --> 00:09:15,875
[STUDENT C]
Typical Fukushina.

180
00:09:15,958 --> 00:09:18,583
Always trying to be Akane's
knight in shining armor.

181
00:09:18,666 --> 00:09:19,583
[STUDENT B]
If you honestly think

182
00:09:19,666 --> 00:09:20,958
its "wrong" and "disrespectful,"

183
00:09:21,041 --> 00:09:23,708
then why are you marching
right along with us?

184
00:09:23,791 --> 00:09:24,750
[KAREN]
Oh, no!

185
00:09:24,833 --> 00:09:26,416
Those dudes have
definitely noticed.

186
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:30,125
Am I going crazy, or is that
horde of boys following us?

187
00:09:30,208 --> 00:09:32,833
[KAREN] She's so oblivious.
And it's kinda adorable.

188
00:09:32,916 --> 00:09:34,000
[KAREN]
Hurry up, Akane!

189
00:09:34,083 --> 00:09:35,291
[MALE STUDENTS]
Sneak a peek.

190
00:09:35,375 --> 00:09:37,000
[KAREN]
They're gaining on us!

191
00:09:37,083 --> 00:09:39,791
I should've told her about
the skirt as soon as I noticed!

192
00:09:39,875 --> 00:09:42,083
If she realizes it's missing
in front of this crowd,

193
00:09:42,166 --> 00:09:44,000
she's gonna have a
serious break down!

194
00:09:44,083 --> 00:09:47,500
And it'll be all my fault
for being a bad friend!

195
00:09:47,583 --> 00:09:49,875
I need to find a way to ditch
these drooling hooligans

196
00:09:49,958 --> 00:09:52,541
and gently tell her the truth
about what's happening.

197
00:09:52,625 --> 00:09:54,750
[KAREN] Kanade!
I'm so glad we found you!

198
00:09:54,833 --> 00:09:56,666
Dear, God! The rumors are true!

199
00:09:56,750 --> 00:09:58,708
You're walking
around pantsless!

200
00:09:58,791 --> 00:09:59,708
No!

201
00:09:59,791 --> 00:10:01,250
[AKANE]
What're you talking about?

202
00:10:01,333 --> 00:10:02,875
Of course I'm wearing something.

203
00:10:02,958 --> 00:10:03,625
What?

204
00:10:03,708 --> 00:10:04,291
[MALE STUDENTS]
What?

205
00:10:04,375 --> 00:10:06,166
[KANADE]
For real?

206
00:10:06,250 --> 00:10:08,041
That's kinda hard to believe.

207
00:10:08,125 --> 00:10:11,083
So, that's why everyone's
been staring at me.

208
00:10:11,166 --> 00:10:14,416
Boys. They can be so ridiculous.

209
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:17,250
Coming to school, I ripped
my skirt on a branch

210
00:10:17,333 --> 00:10:20,166
while hiding from the
surveillance cameras.

211
00:10:22,041 --> 00:10:25,083
Luckily, I found a pair of gym
shorts in the bottom of my bag.

212
00:10:25,166 --> 00:10:27,750
Well, it sounds like something
that would happen to you.

213
00:10:27,833 --> 00:10:29,583
I was getting kinda worried.

214
00:10:29,666 --> 00:10:32,541
I can't believe you thought
I'd come to school half naked.

215
00:10:32,625 --> 00:10:34,750
Sorry, but it did look that way.

216
00:10:34,833 --> 00:10:38,333
[AKANE] Here, I'll prove
it to you. Take a look!

217
00:10:41,166 --> 00:10:43,166
[ALL gasp]

218
00:10:59,333 --> 00:11:01,666
What... the...?

219
00:11:03,166 --> 00:11:04,708
[KAREN]
No matter how you look at them,

220
00:11:04,791 --> 00:11:05,833
they're definitely panties.

221
00:11:05,916 --> 00:11:10,333
