222
00:11:20,750 --> 00:11:22,916
[OFFICER ] And now the student
council Vice President,

223
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:25,666
Kanade Sakurada, will be
making an announcement

224
00:11:25,750 --> 00:11:27,000
in the president's absence.

225
00:11:27,083 --> 00:11:29,458
[STUDENT H] Seriously?
The president's out again?

226
00:11:29,541 --> 00:11:31,041
[STUDENT E] I've been in
the council a long time

227
00:11:31,125 --> 00:11:32,666
and I've never even
seen the president.

228
00:11:32,750 --> 00:11:35,083
[STUDENT F] Me either!
I have no clue who it is.

229
00:11:35,166 --> 00:11:37,375
[STUDENT G] I heard a rumor
that it's a freshman.

230
00:11:37,458 --> 00:11:38,625
[STUDENT J]
Everyone knows they can't become

231
00:11:38,708 --> 00:11:40,000
student council officers.

232
00:11:40,083 --> 00:11:40,833
[STUDENT I]
Oh, really?

233
00:11:40,916 --> 00:11:42,250
[STUDENT K]
Yes, really.

234
00:11:42,333 --> 00:11:43,791
I've heard the prez is short

235
00:11:43,875 --> 00:11:46,291
and that's why everyone
thinks they're a freshman.

236
00:11:47,416 --> 00:11:50,333
First, I've got an
exciting announcement.

237
00:11:50,416 --> 00:11:53,041
Next weekend, our school
will be participating

238
00:11:53,125 --> 00:11:55,375
in the first Community
Clean Up Day.

239
00:11:55,458 --> 00:11:57,000
[AKANE]
"Community Clean Up Day"?

240
00:11:57,083 --> 00:11:58,541
[KANADE]
With a little elbow grease,

241
00:11:58,625 --> 00:12:01,208
we can help our city become
an even more beautiful place

242
00:12:01,291 --> 00:12:02,375
to live.

243
00:12:02,458 --> 00:12:04,750
I look forward to seeing
all of you there.

244
00:12:06,333 --> 00:12:08,083
[AKANE]
Cleaning up the community?

245
00:12:08,166 --> 00:12:10,250
That sounds like torture.

246
00:12:10,333 --> 00:12:11,500
Do you want me to ask Kanade

247
00:12:11,583 --> 00:12:13,333
if the freshman class
can just be in charge

248
00:12:13,416 --> 00:12:15,166
of the beautification
of our school grounds?

249
00:12:15,250 --> 00:12:17,458
No, I shouldn't ask her
for special treatment.

250
00:12:17,541 --> 00:12:19,708
Cleaning up the city'll
make the residents happy

251
00:12:19,791 --> 00:12:22,166
and as a member of the royal
family, I should take part.

252
00:12:22,250 --> 00:12:23,291
[FUKUSHINA]
Huh?

253
00:12:23,375 --> 00:12:24,708
But I'm nervous.

254
00:12:24,791 --> 00:12:27,708
There's gonna be people
helping us that I don't know.

255
00:12:27,791 --> 00:12:29,083
[FUKUSHINA]
This is probably gonna be tough

256
00:12:29,166 --> 00:12:31,333
for Akane since strangers
make her skittish,

257
00:12:31,416 --> 00:12:33,000
but it's gonna be great for me!

258
00:12:33,083 --> 00:12:34,958
She's so cute when
she gets embarrassed.

259
00:12:35,041 --> 00:12:37,500
I'd die a happy man if I could
stare at that flustered face

260
00:12:37,583 --> 00:12:38,666
for the rest of my life.

261
00:12:38,750 --> 00:12:39,375
[TAKEDA]
President!

262
00:12:39,458 --> 00:12:40,708
[FUKUSHINA]
Hm?

263
00:12:40,791 --> 00:12:42,375
We really need to discuss
this morning's meeting.

264
00:12:42,458 --> 00:12:43,583
[FUKUSHINA]
Are you sure that's something

265
00:12:43,666 --> 00:12:46,375
you need to discuss
with me, Takeda?

266
00:12:47,750 --> 00:12:48,833
Hi, Miss Sakurada!

267
00:12:48,916 --> 00:12:51,208
Hi! How's your day
going so far, Takeda?

268
00:12:51,291 --> 00:12:52,708
Sorry, but I've gotta run.

269
00:12:52,791 --> 00:12:55,500
Apparently the seniors need
me for some unknown reason.

270
00:12:55,583 --> 00:12:56,750
Do you mind taking these for me?

271
00:12:56,833 --> 00:12:58,333
Sure. Of course.

272
00:12:58,416 --> 00:13:01,083
[FUKUSHINA] All right, now let's
go see what's so important.

273
00:13:01,166 --> 00:13:03,333
[AKANE] Why would a senior
need to talk to Fukushina

274
00:13:03,416 --> 00:13:05,125
about the student
council meeting?

275
00:13:05,208 --> 00:13:07,291
And why did he call
him "president"?

276
00:13:07,375 --> 00:13:09,791
What in the world
is going on with him?

277
00:13:11,916 --> 00:13:13,666
[FUKUSHINA] How many times
do I have to tell you

278
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:15,666
not to call me
"president" at school?

279
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:17,250
[TAKEDA]
I'm sorry, sir.

280
00:13:17,333 --> 00:13:19,250
I promise it won't happen again.

281
00:13:19,333 --> 00:13:20,666
[FUKUSHINA]
Please see that it doesn't.

282
00:13:20,750 --> 00:13:22,541
You're right though,
Akane is stressed out

283
00:13:22,625 --> 00:13:24,500
about the upcoming
community clean up.

284
00:13:24,583 --> 00:13:27,916
We need to devise a plan to
get her out of participating.

285
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,916
What genius came up
with this dumb project?

286
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,833
[FUKUSHINA]
I'm sure it was Kanade.

287
00:13:31,916 --> 00:13:33,916
She seems to run
the council nowadays.

288
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,208
[MEMBER A]
I know!

289
00:13:35,291 --> 00:13:36,958
Let's gather some students
and start a protest!

290
00:13:37,041 --> 00:13:38,291
[FUKUSHINA]
Bad idea.

291
00:13:38,375 --> 00:13:40,708
It would draw even more
unwanted attention to us.

292
00:13:40,791 --> 00:13:43,166
[MEMBER B]
Then what are we going to do?

293
00:13:43,250 --> 00:13:44,583
Don't worry, gents.

294
00:13:44,666 --> 00:13:46,750
Fukushina is on the case.

295
00:13:46,833 --> 00:13:48,208
[STUDENT L]
Hey, Kanade!

296
00:13:48,291 --> 00:13:50,666
There's a freshman
asking for you!

297
00:13:50,750 --> 00:13:51,833
'Kay.

298
00:13:51,916 --> 00:13:53,208
[STUDENT D]
Oh, is that a new boyfriend?

299
00:13:53,291 --> 00:13:56,875
Yeah, right, like I would
date an underclassman.

300
00:13:56,958 --> 00:14:00,416
Hey, check it out. Some kid's
hittin' on your sister.

301
00:14:03,416 --> 00:14:04,666
The president?

302
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:05,833
[YAMAMOTO]
Huh?

303
00:14:05,916 --> 00:14:08,916
Nothing. Just thinkin'.
Everything's cool.

304
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,166
If you say so.

305
00:14:10,250 --> 00:14:12,083
Hey, you know the
community clean up thing

306
00:14:12,166 --> 00:14:13,958
happening this weekend?

307
00:14:14,041 --> 00:14:16,458
It's really lame.
Ask Kana to call it off.

308
00:14:16,541 --> 00:14:17,083
Sure.

309
00:14:17,166 --> 00:14:18,583
Wow, really?

310
00:14:18,666 --> 00:14:20,166
[SHU] There's only
one reason the president

311
00:14:20,250 --> 00:14:21,583
would need to talk to Kanade.

312
00:14:21,666 --> 00:14:23,666
Something's up with Akane.

313
00:14:23,750 --> 00:14:25,750
So, what is it you
want this time?

314
00:14:25,833 --> 00:14:27,208
As you might've suspected,

315
00:14:27,291 --> 00:14:29,458
I've got issues with this
"community clean up."

316
00:14:29,541 --> 00:14:32,291
Of course you do, and you think
Akane'll feel more comfortable

317
00:14:32,375 --> 00:14:34,125
if she sticks to cleaning
the school grounds.

318
00:14:34,208 --> 00:14:35,041
Correct.

319
00:14:35,125 --> 00:14:36,333
Not gonna happen.

320
00:14:36,416 --> 00:14:37,875
[FUKUSHINA]
Uh.

321
00:14:37,958 --> 00:14:39,791
[KANADE] I won't take pity on
her. She owes me 40 million.

322
00:14:39,875 --> 00:14:41,041
[FUKUSHINA]
Uh?

323
00:14:41,125 --> 00:14:43,041
You're looking at this
the wrong way though.

324
00:14:43,125 --> 00:14:45,541
Akane's gonna have to work with
strangers during the clean up

325
00:14:45,625 --> 00:14:47,250
and that's gonna make
her super nervous.

326
00:14:47,333 --> 00:14:49,500
That's precisely what I've
been trying to tell you!

327
00:14:49,583 --> 00:14:51,833
You like it when she gets
all flustered, don'tcha?

328
00:14:51,916 --> 00:14:54,333
You think it's cute.

329
00:14:54,416 --> 00:14:56,166
[FUKUSHINA]
She's got my number all right.

330
00:14:56,250 --> 00:14:58,375
Embarrassed Akane
is my favorite.

331
00:14:58,458 --> 00:15:01,208
Nothing could beat a whole
day of watching her blush.

332
00:15:02,291 --> 00:15:04,375
[KANADE]
Well, that was easy.

333
00:15:10,541 --> 00:15:12,583
[AKANE] I wonder what
Fukushina is up to.

334
00:15:12,666 --> 00:15:15,083
Oh, I spot a cute little
red-headed princess.

335
00:15:15,166 --> 00:15:16,625
[AKANE yelps]

336
00:15:18,791 --> 00:15:21,583
Hey, Sakurada's sister's here!

337
00:15:23,875 --> 00:15:25,041
Hello, Akane!

338
00:15:25,125 --> 00:15:25,916
Hi, Sato!

339
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:28,125
What'd I miss? Oh, hi, Princess.

340
00:15:30,333 --> 00:15:32,041
Did ya want me to
grab your brother?

341
00:15:32,125 --> 00:15:33,291
Or maybe your sister?

342
00:15:33,375 --> 00:15:34,833
Well, uh.

343
00:15:34,916 --> 00:15:37,708
[HITOMI] Ha. I doubt she wants
to talk to Shu. Nobody does.

344
00:15:37,791 --> 00:15:39,250
What? Why would you say that?

345
00:15:39,333 --> 00:15:42,666
She's clearly joking. C'mon,
let's hang out with Akane!

346
00:15:45,708 --> 00:15:46,833
[SHU]
Hey, Kanade.

347
00:15:46,916 --> 00:15:47,916
[KANADE]
Hm?

348
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,958
Whoa, what's with
the furrowed brow?

349
00:15:50,041 --> 00:15:51,916
What were you and the
president talking about?

350
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:53,958
The usual, Akane's
hand in marriage.

351
00:15:54,041 --> 00:15:55,208
That dweeb has some nerve

352
00:15:55,291 --> 00:15:56,875
if he thinks I'd ever
allow that to happen!

353
00:15:56,958 --> 00:15:58,500
You can't just marry
a Sakurada on a whim!

354
00:15:58,583 --> 00:15:59,958
We're royalty,
for crying out loud!

355
00:16:00,041 --> 00:16:01,208
Relax, I'm kidding.

356
00:16:01,291 --> 00:16:02,583
We were talking
about the cleanup.

357
00:16:02,666 --> 00:16:04,125
Oh, good. I was worried
it was something important.

358
00:16:04,208 --> 00:16:05,083
You're a jerk!

359
00:16:05,166 --> 00:16:06,416
So?

360
00:16:06,500 --> 00:16:08,125
Did you get a chance to
clear the air with Kanade?

361
00:16:08,208 --> 00:16:09,166
[SHU]
Huh?

362
00:16:09,250 --> 00:16:11,000
Oh yeah, I just had
a chat with her.

363
00:16:11,083 --> 00:16:12,250
[SHU]
About Akane's fan boy.

364
00:16:12,333 --> 00:16:14,375
Awesome! I knew you'd
change her mind!

365
00:16:14,458 --> 00:16:18,041
[YAMAMOTO] Kanade's not
stealing my weekend. No way!

366
00:16:18,125 --> 00:16:21,291
Uzuki, are you feeling
okay? Need anything?

367
00:16:21,375 --> 00:16:25,125
Nah, I'll be fine, but
thanks for the tissue.

368
00:16:25,208 --> 00:16:29,000
[SHIZURU] Hey, Aoi, there's
a freshman here asking for ya.

369
00:16:29,083 --> 00:16:30,583
As much as I would love to see

370
00:16:30,666 --> 00:16:33,583
Akane get all cute and flustered
during the cleanup, I'm torn.

371
00:16:33,666 --> 00:16:36,625
As president, I feel like it's
my obligation to protect her.

372
00:16:36,708 --> 00:16:38,625
I don't want to act
like a selfish leader.

373
00:16:38,708 --> 00:16:40,416
Um, you know what I'm saying?

374
00:16:40,500 --> 00:16:42,000
[AOI]
Uh.

375
00:16:42,083 --> 00:16:44,916
[AOI] Is he asking me to make
some sort of a decision for him?

376
00:16:46,083 --> 00:16:50,041
Well, honestly, it's not your
place to make that decision.

377
00:16:50,125 --> 00:16:53,333
It's up to Akane,
so let her decide.

378
00:16:53,416 --> 00:16:56,583
And I happen to know that Akane
plans on giving it her all,

379
00:16:56,666 --> 00:16:58,625
despite the fact that
she's feeling nervous.

380
00:16:58,708 --> 00:16:59,791
If you're a good friend,

381
00:16:59,875 --> 00:17:01,125
you'll let her work
through her anxiety.

382
00:17:01,208 --> 00:17:02,750
Besides, you and I both know,

383
00:17:02,833 --> 00:17:04,708
participating in this
will be good for her.

384
00:17:04,791 --> 00:17:08,000
Yes. Of course you're right.
I'll stand by m'lady.

385
00:17:08,083 --> 00:17:10,333
I'll only offer my
assistance if she needs it.

386
00:17:10,416 --> 00:17:12,833
'Kay! I'll inform the club.

387
00:17:12,916 --> 00:17:14,250
Thank you for all of your help.

388
00:17:14,333 --> 00:17:17,291
I feel good about this
decision. I'll see you later.

389
00:17:17,375 --> 00:17:20,291
[AOI] I guess I gave him
the answer he wanted to hear.

390
00:17:20,375 --> 00:17:23,625
[NANAO]
Aoi, you sure are popular today.

391
00:17:23,708 --> 00:17:24,458
[AOI gasps]

392
00:17:24,541 --> 00:17:26,166
[AOI]
Akane?

393
00:17:26,250 --> 00:17:28,416
What a surprise, you
never visit my class.

394
00:17:28,500 --> 00:17:29,791
Is everything okay?

395
00:17:29,875 --> 00:17:32,541
So, um, just curious,
aren't you like good friends

396
00:17:32,625 --> 00:17:34,291
with the student
council president?

397
00:17:34,375 --> 00:17:37,208
Of course I am. We've been
friends for a long time now.

398
00:17:37,291 --> 00:17:39,416
So, the president
is a senior then?

399
00:17:39,500 --> 00:17:41,708
Yes, definitely.

400
00:17:41,791 --> 00:17:43,083
Is that all you wanted?

401
00:17:43,166 --> 00:17:44,583
Well, no.

402
00:17:44,666 --> 00:17:47,166
There's one more thing I need
from you. Please help me!

403
00:17:47,250 --> 00:17:48,250
[UZUKI]
Huh?

404
00:17:48,333 --> 00:17:50,166
Why do you keep
running away from us?

405
00:17:50,250 --> 00:17:52,791
Yeah, you know we'll
always find you.

406
00:17:55,333 --> 00:17:57,708
[FUKUSHINA] I've decided
that we will be participating

407
00:17:57,791 --> 00:17:58,875
in the community clean up.

408
00:17:58,958 --> 00:17:59,833
[MEMBER B]
But I thought that we all agreed

409
00:17:59,916 --> 00:18:01,041
it was a bad idea!

410
00:18:01,125 --> 00:18:03,250
Do you not remember
our club's sole purpose?

411
00:18:03,333 --> 00:18:05,708
We swore to respect,
honor, and cherish her.

412
00:18:05,791 --> 00:18:08,583
To act in her well-being in
any and every circumstance,

413
00:18:08,666 --> 00:18:10,500
regardless of the personal cost.

414
00:18:10,583 --> 00:18:13,708
That's the goal of the
Princess Akane Fan Club!

415
00:18:13,791 --> 00:18:15,041
You hear me?!

416
00:18:15,125 --> 00:18:17,250
As secret admirers we
must follow those tenets,

417
00:18:17,333 --> 00:18:18,583
it is our duty!

418
00:18:18,666 --> 00:18:20,208
Hold up there, Mr. President,

419
00:18:20,291 --> 00:18:21,791
I thought we were all
supposed to help make

420
00:18:21,875 --> 00:18:23,625
our princess's life
more peaceful.

421
00:18:23,708 --> 00:18:26,416
Not put her through this kinda
unnecessary embarrassment.

422
00:18:26,500 --> 00:18:28,666
This project will
upset her, sir!

423
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:29,750
[FUKUSHINA]
Quiet, Takeda.

424
00:18:29,833 --> 00:18:31,458
It's our responsibility
to support Akane

425
00:18:31,541 --> 00:18:33,000
in all of her endeavors.

426
00:18:33,083 --> 00:18:35,458
She wants to participate
in the community clean up,

427
00:18:35,541 --> 00:18:37,458
so we'll be there
working alongside her.

428
00:18:37,541 --> 00:18:38,791
[MEMBER C]
But, President,

429
00:18:38,875 --> 00:18:40,166
she's gonna be surrounded
by hundreds of people

430
00:18:40,250 --> 00:18:42,208
and they're all gonna be
staring at her all day long!

431
00:18:42,291 --> 00:18:43,750
Yes, I know.

432
00:18:43,833 --> 00:18:45,916
But she wants to do this to
overcome her crippling shyness.

433
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:47,958
As club members we must
offer her our support

434
00:18:48,041 --> 00:18:49,791
during this challenging time.

435
00:18:49,875 --> 00:18:52,250
This is madness. She's not
ready to face the public,

436
00:18:52,333 --> 00:18:53,583
dontcha think she's
moving too fast?

437
00:18:53,666 --> 00:18:55,083
Yea probably, but
we'll get the chance

438
00:18:55,166 --> 00:18:57,083
to see her blush when she's
embarrassed and stuff.

439
00:18:57,166 --> 00:18:59,250
[ALL]
Uh...

440
00:19:00,291 --> 00:19:01,583
Oh, boy.

441
00:19:01,666 --> 00:19:04,333
I never should've gone into
the seniors' classrooms.

442
00:19:04,416 --> 00:19:07,541
I give up. I'm done
looking for Fukushina.

443
00:19:07,625 --> 00:19:08,250
Uh?

444
00:19:08,333 --> 00:19:09,458
How'd he end up here?

445
00:19:09,541 --> 00:19:10,791
Hey, where've you been?

446
00:19:10,875 --> 00:19:13,083
Thanks for dealing with
those books for me.

447
00:19:13,166 --> 00:19:15,583
Oh! Sure!
It wasn't a big deal!

448
00:19:15,666 --> 00:19:18,666
[AKANE] But why'd her run off
earlier? It can't hurt to ask.

449
00:19:18,750 --> 00:19:22,791
About that, is everything okay
with your friend Takeda?

450
00:19:22,875 --> 00:19:26,500
Yeah. Everything's fine.

451
00:19:26,583 --> 00:19:28,416
[FUKUSHINA] I need to make
sure my camcorder is charged

452
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:30,791
and ready to capture
this weekend.

453
00:19:33,208 --> 00:19:34,458
[UZUKI]
All right, everyone!

454
00:19:34,541 --> 00:19:36,166
Let's show the community
how much we care

455
00:19:36,250 --> 00:19:38,583
by making our town
squeaky clean!

456
00:19:38,666 --> 00:19:40,416
[STUDENTS]
Okay!

457
00:19:40,500 --> 00:19:41,625
[UZUKI]
Phew.

458
00:19:41,708 --> 00:19:43,875
[KANADE]
Way to rally the troops!

459
00:19:43,958 --> 00:19:46,458
Are you feeling okay
today, President Uzuki?

460
00:19:46,541 --> 00:19:49,708
Yeah. I actually haven't
felt this good in a while.

461
00:19:49,791 --> 00:19:51,583
I'm sorry that you've had
to fill in as president

462
00:19:51,666 --> 00:19:52,750
so much lately.

463
00:19:52,833 --> 00:19:54,833
No prob. It's my job, after all.

464
00:19:54,916 --> 00:19:56,666
Hey, Shu, my so-called friend!

465
00:19:56,750 --> 00:19:58,708
What happened to Kanade
cancelling this clean up?

466
00:19:58,791 --> 00:20:00,041
You told me I wouldn't
have to do this...

467
00:20:00,125 --> 00:20:02,083
What the heck is he
shouting about over there?

468
00:20:02,166 --> 00:20:05,875
I think he's completely
lost it. Keep it down, man!

469
00:20:05,958 --> 00:20:10,958
Um. Okay, class. Do your best
to pick up all of the trash.

470
00:20:11,041 --> 00:20:12,333
Is everybody ready?!

471
00:20:12,416 --> 00:20:13,875
[FRESHMAN]
Yeah!

472
00:20:13,958 --> 00:20:15,958
Let's show 'em freshman
class is the best!

473
00:20:16,041 --> 00:20:17,458
We'll have fun.

474
00:20:17,541 --> 00:20:19,750
And we'll pick up more trash
than all the upperclassmen!

475
00:20:19,833 --> 00:20:21,666
Remember, Akane's our class rep,

476
00:20:21,750 --> 00:20:25,500
so our actions will reflect
upon her. Don't screw this up!

477
00:20:25,583 --> 00:20:26,750
[FRESHMAN]
Yes, sir!

478
00:20:26,833 --> 00:20:28,583
[AKANE] Who'd've thought
Fukushina cared so much

479
00:20:28,666 --> 00:20:30,833
about this community clean up.

480
00:20:37,916 --> 00:20:40,916
[AKANE] I'm so tired.
I could sleep forever.

481
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,875
[KANADE]
You're too young to be so tired.

482
00:20:42,958 --> 00:20:44,583
You did this to me.

483
00:20:44,666 --> 00:20:47,375
I'm emotionally drained from
being in the public eye all day.

484
